column9: description:{"en":"At first glance the story is simply about Locke. He has no family name; when asked \"Locke what?\" he replies \"Just Locke.\" His genesis is before the \"Cosmic Year\" calendar used in the story. Although there are rumors that the author has an origin in mind for Locke
column10: it is still a mystery to readers as well as to the other characters in the story. All of the stories deal either directly with Locke or with actions only slightly removed from him. The primary plot deals with Locke's involvement in struggles against evil of one sort or another—either human or quasi-supernatural. Frequently Locke is drawn into events that are happening around him. Either he stumbles onto a situation that his heart will not let him ignore
column11: or one of the other players begs him to join their cause. Sometimes he relents and joins their cause; sometimes he ends up opposing them.  \n  \nAs the story slowly grows around the reader (and there is a lot of story!) he finds that it is a chronology of human history in the future. column39: 비라는 곰 가족 ‘보로’와 사람의 손길이 닿지 않는 깊은 숲속에서 꿋꿋하게 살아간다.\n\n어느 날 계곡에서 낚시를 하던 비라는 북천마교에게 쫓겨 위기에 빠진 ‘탄유’라고 불리는 청년과 마주치게 되고
column40:
자신과는 다르게 자신의 목숨이 위태로운 상황에서도 비라를 챙기는 탄유의 모습에서 옛 할아버지의 모습을 보게 된다.

결국 비라는 ‘사람들의 인생에 끼어들지 말라’는 할아버지의 가르침을 어기고 탄유를 위험 속에서 도와주고
column41: 이 인연으로 두 사람은 친구이자 의형제가 된다.\n\n하지만 탄유는 비라가 잠든 사이 북천마교의 교주를 만나 꼭 확인해야 할 일이 있다며
column42:
다시 돌아오겠다는 말을 남기고 훌쩍 떠나는데……

탄유가 향한 곳은 ‘통곡의 폐허’라 불리는 위험지역.

잠에서 깬 비라는 보로에게 탄유의 위험한 상황을 듣게 되고
column43:
망설임 끝에 숲에서 기다리라는 할아버지의 유언을 뒤로 한 채 
탄유를 구하기 위해 숲속을 벗어나 세상 밖으로 나간다. 


인간들의 전쟁과 무림의 혈투가 소용돌이치는 난세 속으로 몸을 던지는 비라의 모험담이 펼쳐진다!

column44: ru:"Главный герой Бира жил счастливой жизнью
column45: скитаясь по свету и наслаждаясь рыбалкой со своим дедушкой. Однажды дедушка внезапно пропал
column46: предварительно сказав Бире идти в лес
column48: и ждать его там. Дед учил своего внука не лезть в жизнь других людей и не принимать от них никаких даров и подарков. Храня эти уроки в сердце
column49: Биру удалось без труда выжить в глубине дремучего леcа
column51: и даже подружить с медведицей по имени Боро. Как-то раз Бира рыбачил в одной из долин леса
column52: где внезапно наткнулся на молодого парня по имени Таню
column53: попавшего в неприятности. В нём он увидел нечто до боли знакомое. В итоге Бира впервые жизни проигнорировал слова деда о невмешательстве в чужие жизни и решил помочь парню в трудной ситуации. Так между ними завязались дружеские и даже отчасти братские отношения. Однако уже вскоре
column59: и он скоро вернётся… Таню направился в опасную местность под названием «Руины плача». Проснувшийся Бира
column65: с просьбой подождать его возвращения в лесу
column68: отправился во внешний мир на поиски Таню. Так начались его приключения в хаотичном мире
column69: раздираемом бесконечными людскими дрязгами и битвами ни на жизнь
column70:
а на смерть.

column73:
zh-hk:"主角「飛羅」喜歡和爺爺一起去釣魚，
兩人以四海為家，過著幸福快樂的生活。
某天，爺爺卻突然丟下一句話，
要飛羅前往北方邊境的森林等他回來，
旋即消失得無影無蹤。

飛羅把爺爺的告誡牢記在心：
「絕對不要干涉他人的人生、
也不要接受他人的好意。」
和熊「波魯」一家在杳無人煙的深山裡
堅強地生活著。

有一天，在溪谷釣魚的飛羅，
遇見了被北川魔教追趕、陷入危機的「譚裕」。
他在即便自身難保，
也還是一心想保護別人的譚裕身上，
看見了過往爺爺的影子。
最後，飛羅違背了爺爺「不干預他人人生」的信念，
從危難中救出了譚裕，
兩人因此成為了朋友以及結拜兄弟。

然而，譚裕為了向北川魔教教主確認某事，
趁著飛羅睡著時，承諾自己會再回來，便悄然離去...
而他的目的地就是危險地帶「慟哭之墟」。

飛羅一覺醒來，從波魯口中得知譚裕深陷危險。
經過百般猶豫，將爺爺要他等待的遺言拋諸腦後。
為了拯救譚裕，他離開了森林、走向外面的世界。

於是，
飛羅就在人類的戰爭以及腥風血雨的武林亂世中，
展開了他的冒險!

column13: description:{"en":"Renton is a 14-year-old boy who occasionally helps out his grandfather as a mechanic. But his feelings of dissatisfaction and frustration grow as his mundane and routine work cloud his visions for his future
column14: and he dreams of flying around the world. One day
column15: a mysterious UFO falls from the sky. On board was a girl named Eureka
column16: and the encounter with her changes Renton's destiny drastically..."
column17: id:"Renton Thurston seorang anak muda berusia 14 tahun yang lelah dengan kehidupannya yang monoton. Perasaan frustasinya datang dari kehidupan keras sebagai mekanik di bengkel kakeknya dan menjadi anak dari pahlawan legendaris yang misterius. Satu hal yang membuat Renton senang adalah ketika dia berselancar
column18: olah raga ekstrim sejenis hover-boarding di udara.\nSuatu hari sebuah LFO (Light Finding Operation) bernama Nirvash jatuh dan dari dalam muncul gadis bernama Eureka yang meminta tolong memperbaiki Nirvash. Ketika Renton yang tergila-gila jatuh cinta padanya dan membantu memperbaiki Nirvash
column19: keduanya memulai petualangan yang akan mengubah takdir mereka berdua..."}

column2: title:{"en":"Dealing With the Prince of Misfortune"}
column7: reincarnates into a frail body in ancient times. The original good-for-nothing host is not only ugly
column8: but her birth father favors the concubine more than the wife
column9: birth mother was framed with adultery and stripped of her rank
column10: twin brother was poisoned by her second mother
column11: her fiance and concubine-sister hooked up and worked together to bring about her tragic death. After Xiao Lingyun is reincarnated
column12: she uses secret techniques of Feng Shui to get back at those who had previously ridiculed and abused her. From the lowest of low to the highest peak of cultivation
column13: she flies towards the immortal realm."}

column25: description:{"en":"The archmage who ruled over a magic kingdom. One day
column26:
she was reborn as the youngest daughter of the empire!

"I'll just play along and pretend to be a baby. …But don’t you think you guys like me a little too much?"

They won't leave her alone. The youngest princess is tired today as well.

---
Princess Enisha's birth marks the start of the Hyperion Empire's prophetic reign. With her unfathomably cute face and a ceaseless supply of loyal servants
column27: life is pretty great for the baby princess. There's just the small issue of her two psychotic-killer brothers and a war-hungry father who she must stop from driving the empire into ruin. Enisha's got a lot on her plate
column28: between the constant flood of assassins trying to kill her and those pesky memories of her past life. But she's in no rush to return to being the powerful high mage of a magical kingdom. After all
column29: being Hyperion's one great hope certainly has its royal perks. It's not easy being the empire's beloved princess
column30:
but these subjects will just have to do.

---

column36: elle se retrouve dans le corps de la petite princesse du royaume voisin d'Hyperion. Or selon la prophétie
column37: elle est l'enfant tant attendue qui apportera gloire et prospérité. Depuis
column38:
elle est dorlotée et adulée par sa nouvelle famille un peu trop protectrice. Arrivera-t-elle à redevenir la Grande Archimage qu'elle était autrefois?

---

column39:

column13: description:{"pt-br":"Um one-shot lançado na edição de abril da JumpSQ em 2017. Conta a história de um Japão onde outros mundos cheios de monstros - apelidados de Dungeons - são simplesmente uma parte normal da vida cotidiana. Funcionários públicos conhecidos como \"Divisão de Captura\" estão encarregados de lidar com eles! Esse Oneshot foi posteriormente serializado na Jump+ sob o nome de Suginami Toubatsu Koumuin: Isekai Kinmu no Hitobito."}

column7: description:{"en":"Nishimiya Kouga is from a distinguished alpha family which puts severe importance on being purebred.\n\nAt work
column8: the person he acknowledges as his rival in business performance is Houjou Misaki
column9: who is also an alpha.\n\nKouga has been putting some distance from his alpha supremacist grandfather
column10: the current head of the Nishimiya clan. But one day
column16: is a distant relative and Kouga has been ordered to care for him. Kouga
column17: despite his disgust with how selfish alphas are
column18: felt pity for the meek and frail-looking Haruto and reluctantly complied.\n\nNow
column19: Kouga is struggling to take care of Haruto who to his surprise

column35: en:"I somehow kidnapped the Grand Duke I had a one-sided love for!\n\nTo hide this fact we had to pretend being in a relationship
column36: but the Grand Duke is behaving strangely:\n\n\"Vivian
column37:
may I kiss you?"

Huh? Are we kissing as soon as we started dating?

"We'll kiss
column38:
then take take a step further and get married."

Is this relationship going to be alright?

---
Vivian Louis is the twenty-one-year-old daughter of a Count
column39: a sweet and seemingly harmless girl who has only one guilty pleasure in life: thirsting after her crush
column40: the breathtakingly handsome Grand Duke Lennox Elphidion Glenn! For her
column41: it was love at first sight at the tender age of fourteen. That’s when she began obsessing over him
column42: creating endless works of fan art and fan fiction. Then one day
column43: an accident with her best friend’s magical crystal ball makes the unthinkable come true. The grand duke is kidnapped and tied up in her bed
column44: and he’s telling her that she’s the kidnapper! Scrambling for a way out of this scandalous bind
column45: the two agree to act like a couple. They even sign a one-year contract
column46: but Lennox seems to want more than a fake relationship. Unbeknownst to Vivian
column47:
a full-blown romance is on its way. Could it be that her wildest fan fantasies will truly come to life?

the story follows an elderly hunter in his attempts to take vengeance on the enormous bear that killed his son.
